commit.message:
Fix time of keymap definition

Keymaps should be defined once when the package is loaded, not every
time the mode is enabled. The correct way allows customizing the
keymap using facilities such as use-package's :bind definitions,
whereas the previous way clobbered any user customizations in the
keymap every time mediawiki-mode was enabled.

Fix time of keymap definition

Keymaps should be defined once when the package is loaded, not every
time the mode is enabled. The correct way allows customizing the
keymap using facilities such as use-package's :bind definitions,
whereas the previous way clobbered any user customizations in the
keymap every time mediawiki-mode was enabled.
